title: Ela Natur
description: A 100% organic gourmet health food store with a large selection of quality fresh fruit and vegetables, as well as regional, baked goods, juices, syrup, wine, gluten-free, lactose-free and vegan organic food. Many different types of grains can be milled to desired spot. A wide range of frozen products and natural toiletries and hygiene products are available. A colorful assortment of over 2,000 items line the shelves. Delivery is offered.
